# game/Scenes/Update20/u20m.rpy:4
translate portuguese u20m_709aec61:

    # "For now, I should go see Reba."
    "Por agora, vou ver a Reba."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20m.rpy:7
translate portuguese u20m_151617f4:

    # "I drive out to Reba's house and knock on her door."
    "Dirijo-me até à casa da Reba e bato à porta."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20m.rpy:8
translate portuguese u20m_349819fa:

    # "I haven't been out here since Mickey was arrested. I hope I'm not about to get shot."
    "Não venho por aqui desde que o Mickey foi preso. Espero não estar prestes a levar um tiro."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20m.rpy:11
translate portuguese u20m_da38ceda:

    # "Reba's mom opens the door, looking at me in disgust."
    "A mãe da Reba abre a porta, olhando para mim com repulsa."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20m.rpy:12
translate portuguese u20m_02882bbf:

    # "Reba's Mom" "You're that college boy that's been hanging around with Reba, ain't ya?"
    "Reba's Mom" "És aquele universitário que anda a sair com a Reba, não és?"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20m.rpy:13
translate portuguese u20m_318f6e59:

    # pc "That's right. Is she home?"
    pc "Exato. Ela está em casa?"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20m.rpy:16
translate portuguese u20m_6b95907a:

    # "Reba's Mom" "What happened with you? She's been all mopey and upset but won't tell me why."
    "Reba's Mom" "O que se passou contigo? Ela anda toda abatida e chateada, mas não me diz porquê."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20m.rpy:17
translate portuguese u20m_e6064c5d:

    # pc "It's... complicated. Can you tell her I'm here?"
    pc "É... complicado. Podes dizer-lhe que estou aqui?"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20m.rpy:18
translate portuguese u20m_8eb00b2c:

    # "Reba's Mom" "Just don't make her sad, okay? She seems happier after she's been with you."
    "Reba's Mom" "Só não a deixes triste, está bem? Ela parece mais feliz depois de estar contigo."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20m.rpy:21
translate portuguese u20m_742064d6:

    # "Reba's Mom" "I like to see her happy."
    "Reba's Mom" "Gosto de a ver feliz."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20m.rpy:22
translate portuguese u20m_6080bf31:

    # "Reba's Mom" "Alright, you can come in. She's asleep in her room."
    "Reba's Mom" "Está bem, podes entrar. Ela está a dormir no quarto dela."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20m.rpy:23
translate portuguese u20m_0558b8ab:

    # "Reba's Mom" "No hanky panky though. Not under my roof."
    "Reba's Mom" "Mas nada de travessuras. Não debaixo do meu teto."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20m.rpy:24
translate portuguese u20m_a9a2d1b9:

    # pc "Thanks."
    pc "Obrigado."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20m.rpy:27
translate portuguese u20m_ac62c564:

    # "I walk quietly into Reba's room. She's in bed, sleeping."
    "Entro silenciosamente no quarto da Reba. Ela está na cama, a dormir."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20m.rpy:30
translate portuguese u20m_a95bfc0c:

    # "Trying not to wake her immediately, I lie next to her and wrap her in my arms."
    "Tentando não a acordar de imediato, deito-me ao lado dela e envolvo-a nos meus braços."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20m.rpy:34
translate portuguese u20m_c981bd85:

    # "She jolts awake and looks at me, shocked."
    "Ela acorda de sobressalto e olha para mim, chocada."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20m.rpy:35
translate portuguese u20m_1542905d:

    # rb "What the heck!? [pcname]!? Am I dreamin'?"
    rb "Mas que raio!? [pcname]!? Estou a sonhar?"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20m.rpy:36
translate portuguese u20m_a64b83f2:

    # pc "No, I'm real. Hey Reba."
    pc "Não, sou real. Olá, Reba."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20m.rpy:39
translate portuguese u20m_b5e336f8:

    # "She leans in and kisses me deeply, her lips soft and warm against mine."
    "Ela inclina-se e beija-me profundamente, os seus lábios macios e quentes contra os meus."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20m.rpy:40
translate portuguese u20m_c73e0cd1:

    # rb "Dang, I missed you."
    rb "Caramba, senti a tua falta."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20m.rpy:43
translate portuguese u20m_a4520e8b:

    # rb "So what the heck happened? Did you see your daddy?"
    rb "Então, o que raio aconteceu? Viste o teu pai?"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20m.rpy:44
translate portuguese u20m_90d868cb:

    # pc "Yeah, everything went like it was supposed to. Mostly."
    pc "Sim, correu tudo como devia. Mais ou menos."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20m.rpy:45
translate portuguese u20m_48ae30e6:

    # pc "I'll tell you all about it tomorrow."
    pc "Conto-te tudo amanhã."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20m.rpy:48
translate portuguese u20m_98b63ab5:

    # rb "I'm just glad you're back."
    rb "Só estou feliz por estares de volta."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20m.rpy:49
translate portuguese u20m_5964ada9:

    # rb "And your hair is all long now. It looks really bad."
    rb "E o teu cabelo está todo comprido agora. Fica mesmo mal."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20m.rpy:50
translate portuguese u20m_a6d4efd9:

    # rb "I kind of like the beard though."
    rb "Mas até gosto da barba."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20m.rpy:53
translate portuguese u20m_6ec05860:

    # rb "I missed kissing you and doing it with you."
    rb "Tive saudades de te beijar e de fazer isso contigo."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20m.rpy:54
translate portuguese u20m_7d4be04f:

    # pc "I missed it too, Reba."
    pc "Também tive saudades, Reba."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20m.rpy:55
translate portuguese u20m_65a81a6c:

    # rb "If we was at your house, I'd do it with you right now. But I don't want Mama to hear us."
    rb "Se estivéssemos em tua casa, fazia isso contigo agora mesmo. Mas não quero que a mamã nos ouça."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20m.rpy:56
translate portuguese u20m_f90984e6:

    # pc "Maybe tomorrow."
    pc "Talvez amanhã."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20m.rpy:57
translate portuguese u20m_6f8fbc94:

    # rb "Definitely."
    rb "Com certeza."

